    <title>Apple will charge more to swap your iPhone 16 Pro battery</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A picture of the iPhone 16 Pro cameras." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D_jNEv2qQa4js_2xEl4gjB_cmxA=/0x0:5568x3712/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73587565/DSC_3103_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Nilay Patel&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="r5Anl9"&gt;Apple has hiked the price of its &lt;a href="https://support.apple.com/iphone/repair/battery-replacement"&gt;battery repair service&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos-features-price"&gt;iPhone 16 Pro and Pro Max&lt;/a&gt;. Now, it will cost $119 to get your battery replaced in either phone — a $20 jump over its older fee. The price remains the same for the standard and “Plus” models, as do those for last year’s phones, &lt;a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/09/15/apple-jacking-up-prices-on-post-applecare-iphone-battery-replacements"&gt;as &lt;em&gt;MacRumors&lt;/em&gt; notes&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="EQprC1"&gt;The company doesn’t seem to have started charging more for other battery replacements yet, but it wouldn’t be unexpected. In 2022, Apple drove the cost of iPhone 14 battery service &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/9/12/23348705/iphone-14-apple-battery-replacement-price"&gt;up by $30 to $99&lt;/a&gt;. Increases for iPad, MacBook, and older iPhone battery repairs &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/1/2/23535428/apple-iphone-ipad-mac-battery-service-replacement-price-increase"&gt;came after that&lt;/a&gt;, and Apple Watches &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/15/23875514/apple-watch-battery-replacement-cost-expensive"&gt;followed suit later&lt;/a&gt;. (One longs for the salad days of battery &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/28/16827248/apple-iphone-battery-replacement-price-slow-down-apology"&gt;drama-induced $29 battery replacements&lt;/a&gt;!)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="DaC3yF"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"How and where to replace your old, depleted iPhone battery","url":"https://www.theverge.com/22679492/iphone-apple-battery-replace-ifixit"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="r90gWB"&gt;Defective batteries are covered...&lt;/p&gt;
